T1  - Application of a method for estimating day of ovulation using urinary estrogen and progesterone metabolites.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1097/00001648-199509000-00015
A1  - Baird, D D
A1  - McConnaughey, D R
A1  - Weinberg, C R
